Welcome to Altai!

to the most beautiful region of Russia

lets see more...

The Republic of Altai is in the highlands of the Altai Mountains in the south of Western Siberia. At its widest points, the republic is 360 km from north to south and 380 km from east to west. The republic borders on the republics of Tyva and Khakassia, the Altai Territory and the Kemerovo Region.
